---

<section class="problem-section" style="background: #F5F0E8; padding: 5rem 2.5rem;">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">

    <div style="margin-bottom: 3.5rem; max-width: 680px;">
      <p
        style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 4px; color: rgba(11,26,46,0.35); text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 1.2rem;"
      >
        The problem
      </p>
      <h2
        style="font-family: 'Vollkorn', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.2vw, 2.5rem); color: #0B1A2E; margin: 0 0 1rem; line-height: 1.2;"
      >
        Two problems. Two specific answers.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- New blocks: visibility, context drift, CLAUDE.md bloat -->
    <div
      class="problem-new-blocks"
      style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem;"
    >

      <!-- Block 1: Visibility -->
      <div style="border-left: 3px solid #C49A2B; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #0B1A2E; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          You have no idea what your agent is doing right now.
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #3D4A5C; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 0.9rem;"
        >
          Your agent is running. Is it stuck? Did it touch files it shouldn't? You won't know until the damage is done.
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #C49A2B; margin: 0;"
        >
          &rarr; Real-time visibility. Every file, every command, as it happens.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 2: Context drift -->
      <div style="border-left: 3px solid #C49A2B; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
        <h3
          style="font-family: 'Vollkorn SC', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #0B1A2E; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.3;"
        >
          Your agent is contradicting itself. You just can't see it.
        </h3>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #3D4A5C; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 0.9rem;"
        >
          After an hour of context, compaction kicks in. The agent forgets its own decisions — and reintroduces code you deleted.{' '}
          <a
            href="https://dev.to/gonewx/the-hidden-cost-of-ai-coding-context-loss-and-how-developers-are-fixing-it-4b0d"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            style="color: rgba(196,154,43,0.6); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px;"
            onmouseover="this.style.color='#C49A2B'"
            onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(196,154,43,0.6)'"
          >documented by 200+ developers &rarr;</a>
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #C49A2B; margin: 0;"
        >
          &rarr; Compaction-proof memory. Decisions persisted locally, never lost.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

</style>
